name: United Express CRJ-700 Night Landing at LAX
description:
Hey everyone, this is my flight from Vancouver on a United Express CRJ-700 Landing at Los Angeles International Airport (KLAX/LAX) during the night. We're landing on runway 24R here, and you can see another plane on final approach for runway 25L or 25R beside us. Anyway, enjoy, and please subscribe!
